    "intro": "Application is where Observation and Interpretation become obedience. Each question is paired with a movement of the chapter — read it slowly, answer it honestly, and let it land on a specific situation. Peter writes to a church already feeling the pressure of being called *Christian* as an insult. The chapter's relevance does not depend on your facing literal persecution; it depends on whether you have made up your mind about suffering before it arrives.",
